{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2918e64b4b","title":"中共中央关于同意处理“二七”惨案元凶赵继贤的意见给华东局的指示","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a51175efa3","index":0,"year":1951,"month":5,"day":23,"articleId":"2918e64b4b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"bc1948f261","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于同意处理“二七”惨案元凶赵继贤的意见给华东局的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"13da5c4dc2","type":"appellation","text":"华东局并中南局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"10eeae7621","type":"paragraph","text":"同意将“二七”惨案元凶赵继贤押解郑州，组织工人控诉后处决。请中南局即派人至苏南提解。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"ff244ef4d6","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央二十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"5bdfc1dec4","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"0088d4a22b","type":"subtitle","text":"华东局关于处理“二七”惨案元凶的请示","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"36f0a12523","type":"subtitle","text":"（一九五一年五月二十一日）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"75aed71d98","type":"appellation","text":"中央并中央公安部：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"a22de067d3","type":"paragraph","text":"据苏南区党委五月十九日报告：“二七”惨案元凶赵继贤已于本月十日为苏州市府逮捕，经初步审讯，赵匪对制造“二七”惨案，镇压工人罢工运动，屠杀工人三四百名等罪行均供认不讳。并建议将赵匪解至发生惨案的原地，发动控诉公审处决，以为死难烈士复仇，并教育工人及广大人民等情。如中央批准这一意见，请告中南局派人来苏南提解，或由苏南派人押送武汉。如何？请电示。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"},{"id":"c8a7cfa50c","type":"paragraph","text":" 华东局五月二十一日","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b"}],"page":{"id":"bc4cfd0b85","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"2918e64b4b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}